# 2D Platformer — Project Configuration

## Project Overview
- **Unity Version:** 2022.3 LTS
- **Render Pipeline:** URP (2D Renderer)
- **Genre:** 2D side-scrolling platformer
- **Target Platform:** PC (Steam) + Console (PS5 / Xbox)
- **Target FPS:** 60 baseline on min-spec; uncapped on high-refresh displays

## Architecture

### Assembly Structure
```
MyGame.Core         — events, pooling, utilities, state machine
MyGame.Gameplay     — player controller, enemies, items, level systems
MyGame.Systems      — audio, save, UI, input
MyGame.Editor       — custom inspectors, level tools
```

### Key Systems
- **Player Controller** — Rigidbody2D-based, coyote time, input buffering, variable jump height
- **State Machine** — generic FSM for player states (Idle, Run, Jump, Fall, WallSlide, Dash)
- **Level System** — Tilemap-based, chunk loading for large levels
- **Enemy AI** — state machine per enemy type (Patrol, Chase, Attack)
- **Collectibles** — object-pooled pickups with magnet effect
- **Checkpoint System** — serializable spawn points with state snapshot

### Scene Structure
- `S_Bootstrap` — persistent services (audio, save, input)
- `S_MainMenu` — title screen, settings
- `S_Level_01` through `S_Level_XX` — game levels (additive loaded)

